ent snapshot collection is\n   209\tbest-effort: if transcript records are accepted but environment collection\n   210\tfails, still write the turn and store a failed snapshot status instead of\n   211\tfailing the whole capture.\n   212\t\n   213\tCandidate fields:\n   214\t\n   215\t- uncommitted worktree files: all tracked and untracked files with uncommitted\n   216\t  changes\n   217\t- stacks: zero, one, or many\n   218\t- branches in each stack\n   219\t- optional review unit for each branch, for example a pull request\n   220\t- commits in each branch\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-20T02:22:44.919Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}